Note: Test import with aliasing

Import { add as sum, multiply as product } from "math_helpers.runa"

Process called "main" takes argc as Integer, argv as Pointer returns Integer:
    Note: Using aliased names
    Let result1 be sum(7, 8)
    Display "7 + 8 = "
    Display result1
    Display "\n"

    Let result2 be product(6, 7)
    Display "6 * 7 = "
    Display result2
    Display "\n"

    Return 0
End Process
